.TH man 1 "26 May 2023"

.SH NAME
.B simple_shell
- Simple shell create in C to interact with a linux operating system.

.SH DESCRIPTION
Shell is a UNIX term for the interactive user interface with an operating system. 

.B Overview

The simple shell is a command that reads lines from either a file or the terminal, interprets them, and generally executes other commands.

Always 0 is success other numbers are failure

.SH

.SH OPTIONS
.B simple_shell
Command options will be typed after the main command followed by a space and a
 '-' symbol.
